title: How to Paint: Snow Tank Camouflage
description:
In this Warhammer Painting video, we'll look at a fun way to paint tank camouflage for a snowy environment using sticky tack and spray paint!   
      
If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it.
